<param name="bgcolor" value="#ffffff"/>
<param name="allowfullscreen" value="true"/>
<embed allowfullscreen="true" bgcolor="#ffffff" height="253" name="FVS" pluginspage='http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer"' src="../16/doctor-appointment-you-have_player.swf?1525629061" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="320"/>
</object>
<br/>
<br/>
Also see: <a href="../d/doctor.htm">DOCTOR</a> for the main (non-initialized) 
version of the sign for "doctor."<br/>
 </p>
<hr color="#800080"/>
<p><br/>
	RESERVATION:<br/>
	This version of "appointment" could be used as
  "reserve,"  "to make a reservation," or "I have
  a reservation."  Use a slight rotational movement of the upper hand 
	and change it from a claw hand into a modified "A" hand (the thumb is 
	slightly wrapped) or a full "S" hand.</p>
<p><br/>
<img border="0" height="220" src="../../signjpegs/a/appointment-reservation1.jpg" width="221"/><img border="0" height="220" src="../../signjpegs/a/appointment-reservation2.jpg" width="221"/><img border="0" height="220" src="../../signjpegs/a/appointment-reservation3.jpg" width="221"/><img border="0" height="220" src="../../signjpegs/a/appointment-reservation4.jpg" width="221"/><img border="0" height="220" src="../../signjpegs/a/appointment-reservation5.jpg" width="221"/></p></font></span>
</blockquote>
